    "attributes": {
        "action": "Prohibit HMO licences being granted for properties near schools",
        "additional_details": "We believe the number of reported incidents is increasing and that more attempted abductions are being spoken about via social media. Children are frightened as are the parents.",
        "background": "So that migrants cannot be housed in HMOs located near or next to schools.",
